     A            IKO10          3A  B 16 48DSPATR(CS)
     A  63                                  DSPATR(RI PC)
      *
     A                                 18  7' 5 ' DSPATR(RI)
     A                                 18 12'THE OLD AND THE NEW PROCESS -
     A                                      JUDGMENT'
     A            IKUBN          1A  B 19 12DSPATR(CS)
     A  64                                  DSPATR(RI PC)
     A                                 19 15'1.ALWAYS,THE LATEST PROCESS'
     A                                 20 15'2.BY A PROCESS CHANGE DAY,-
     A                                      OLD AND NEW JUDGEMENT'
